Basic Qualifications For Consideration
Do you have a basic trade qualification as a support equipment technician
Do you have the ability to satisfy all UAE labor and immigration formalities?
Typical Education/Experience
High school diploma or equivalent and typically 5 or more years’ experience in maintenance of Aerospace support equipment or an equivalent combination of education and experience. Field experience in supporting military airlift is highly desirable. Experience working with International customers would be an advantage. Familiarity with the Arabic culture preferred
Other Job related information
This requisition is for an international, locally hired position located in the United Arab Emirates. Please, list all countries of citizenship you hold. Incumbent must be able to periodically travel, principally in the Middle East but possibly elsewhere as dictated by job requirements. Benefits and pay will be determined at the local level and are not part of Boeing US-based payroll, and will be commensurate with experience and qualifications and in accordance with applicable UAE Law. The employment is subject to the candidate’s ability to satisfy all UAE labor and immigration formalities and to obtain a UAE Security Clearance. The job requisition can be closed early depending on the suitability of the candidates.
